        "link": "https://www.instagram.com/reel/DH9tW7OSEd0/?id=3602234764478138228_65681942658",
        "share_text": "Just a quick flick back through some of the contact sheets for this year. Amazing to work with all of these talented musicians and artists. Cannot wait to keep on capture live music. 40 rolls in 4 months and counting \u00f0\u009f\u00a4\u00af All processed and developed by hand. \n\nBig thanks to all the venues for having me @kingstreetnewcastle @hamiltonstationhotel @thelassogowrie @theoak.tigheshill @stagandhunter @hordernpavilion \nAnd huge thanks to all the bands for booking me and letting me shoot you. (Way too many to tag soz) \n\n@ilfordphoto best film/chemicals in the game too!! \n\nIf you\u00e2\u0080\u0099d like me to shoot your band or you are a creative artist and would like some portraits HMU \u00f0\u009f\u00a4\u0099 affordable rates and packages let work together \u00f0\u009f\u0099\u008f \n\n#livemusic #pentax67 #120film #pentax #concertphotography #filmphotography #analogphotography #35mm #newcastle #portraitphotography #blackandwhite",
